result.title: Different answer on problem 731/C
result.content:
I am trying to submit an answer for the problem in Go.

I get correct answer on my computer using Go v1.7.3(which is same as codeforces). Though when I submit the file codeforces calculates the value incorrectly.

Submission here http://codeforces.com/contest/731/submission/22050139.

Could anyone guide me as to why this might be happening?
